        "content": "<p>Over at <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/doc-gen/pull/163\">doc-gen#163</a>, I've tried a rough attempt at showing what instances are available for a given type. See the PR comments for some screenshots (edit: or below):</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib_docs_demo/find/alg_equiv\"><code>alg_equiv</code></a></th>\n<th><a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib_docs_demo/find/monoid_algebra\"><code>monoid_algebra</code></a></th>\n<th><a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib_docs_demo/find/nat\"><code>nat</code></a></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/425260/161541377-5888d4a8-77ac-46d8-8142-725c3adc590f.png\">image</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/425260/161540836-d2b33b69-1027-42fc-ae71-69728fd08d8c.png\">image</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/425260/161541526-d2efe9d4-64b8-4815-9e61-f100c379097b.png\">image</a> ...</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/425260/161541377-5888d4a8-77ac-46d8-8142-725c3adc590f.png\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://uploads.zulipusercontent.net/d5bcd583e9f1b261f825e2bf0760550d8c172838/68747470733a2f2f757365722d696d616765732e67697468756275736572636f6e74656e742e636f6d2f3432353236302f3136313534313337372d35383838643461382d373761632d343664382d383134322d3732356333616463353930662e706e67\"></a></div><div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/425260/161540836-d2b33b69-1027-42fc-ae71-69728fd08d8c.png\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://uploads.zulipusercontent.net/0eef8905bee64007b541457e41725521c534ad47/68747470733a2f2f757365722d696d616765732e67697468756275736572636f6e74656e742e636f6d2f3432353236302f3136313534303833362d64326233336236392d313032372d343266632d616537312d3639373